        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-11-16 08:15:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n> \n> Hi,\n> the chapter hierarchy seems not to work (e.g. subchapters of \"Integration repositories\"),\n\nnot sure to get the point\nOn the preview I see the structure: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/rtdv3-global-verify-master/2642/docs/#\n\n\n> also I would suggest to add the Release Notes as a chapter.\n\nOK I will add it at the beginning\n\n> Best regards\n> Andreas",
